text: Nocardioides ginsengisegetis is a Gram-positive, rod-shaped and non-spore- forming bacterium from the genus of Nocardioides which has been isolated from soil from a ginseng field in Pocheon in Korea. == References == ==External links== *Type strain of Nocardioides ginsengisegetis at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase ginsengisegetis Category:Bacteria described in 2011
title: Nocardioides ginsengisegetis
